main event: An object in the sky resembling a star was observed for 1.5 hours and confirmed as the planet Jupiter the following night.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 1 hour and 30 minutes,The object was initially thought to be a star,The object made a whirring or buzzing sound,At one point, it was reported that there were two objects observed,The witness was sitting on a porch when the object was first noticed.
